path.id: Sri Lanka's Seven Virgins mountains rise like green giants, their seven peaks whispering stories of star sisters and hidden beauty. Lush rainforest cloaks them, guarding secrets of waterfalls and playful monkeys. Though a tragic plane crash once touched their slopes, today, hikers tread gently, seeking adventure and breathtaking views that stretch forever. So, if you crave fresh air and challenges, the Seven Virgins beckon, ready to unveil their magic.
